title: Profile and optimize command startup latency
description: "Follow-up from 2026-05-10 dogfood audit: core agent-loop commands still take roughly 0.5-1.7s in an isolated temp project. Profile startup/runtime initialization, defer nonessential work for read-only commands, and add an automated dogfood benchmark with thresholds."
